=== Noun ===
'''jibber''' ([[jibbers]])

#a horse that [[Jib|jibs]], i.e. refuses, stops short.
#someone who backs out of plans at the last minute, often with a poor excuse (like going to the post office), disappointing others.
# By extension, this term applies to all those who never turn up when invited.

